{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019JczZpknVSRnqAffwUJnQe","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t[Task decomp-test-002-question-child-5] PHASE 3b: IMPLEMENT\n2\tTitle: Undo/redo system for graph edits\n3\t\n4\tRead your plan at .fleet/tasks/decomp-test-002-question-child-5/plan.json.\n5\t\n6\tYOU MUST IMPLEMENT the plan completely. This is the critical execution phase.\n7\t\n8\tFor EACH step in plan.json, you MUST:\n9\t1. Announce: \"=== Step N: {task description} ===\"\n10\t2. Execute the step — create/modify the actual source files\n11\t3. Verify it worked (check file exists, run code, test passes)\n12\t4. Announce: \"=== Step N complete ===\" before moving to next\n13\t\n14\tDO NOT STOP until ALL steps are executed and verified.\n15\tDO NOT just read the plan — you must CREATE the files it specifies.\n16\t\n17\tDEPENDENCIES: Fresh worktree — install before testing:\n18\t  - Node: pnpm install or npm install\n19\t  - Python: pip install -r requirements.txt\n20\t\n21\tAfter all steps are complete, write .fleet/tasks/decomp-test-002-question-child-5/implementation.json:\n22\t{\n23\t  \"phase\": \"implement\",\n24\t  \"steps_completed\": [\n25\t    { \"step\": 1, \"task\": \"...\", \"files_created\": [\"...\"], \"files_modified\": [\"...\"], \"verified\": true }\n26\t  ],\n27\t  \"all_steps_done\": true\n28\t}\n29\t\n30\tBEFORE YOU STOP: git add -A && git commit --no-verify -m \"execute: decomp-test-002-question-child-5\""}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"79b66f7c-c2e7-4ea1-bea2-f0ef0430de4d","uuid":"1fddf2d0-37a3-4be5-a024-1f6694870a99","timestamp":"2026-04-11T21:28:32.516Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/tmp/temporal-worktrees/task-decomp-test-002-question-child-5/.fleet/tasks/decomp-test-002-question-child-5/prompt.txt","content":"[Task decomp-test-002-question-child-5] PHASE 3b: IMPLEMENT\nTitle: Undo/redo system for graph edits\n\nRead your plan at .fleet/tasks/decomp-test-002-question-child-5